    "system": {
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em>You hold your hand in front of you as if holding a ball and hum a single low note. Creatures within the area of silence hear ringing in their ears and then nothing.</em></p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Area Hazard:</strong> No sound can enter or escape the zone of silence and no sound can be heard within. Any creature or object within the sphere is immune to &amp;reference[thunder] damage. All creatures are &amp;reference[deafened] and &amp;reference[silenced] while inside. Casting a spell that includes a verbal component is impossible there.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> The radius of the spell increases by 5 ft. for each spell level above 2nd level.</p>",
            "chat": "<strong>Utility Spell</strong> </p><ul><li><p><strong>Area Hazard:</strong> No sound can enter or escape the zone of silence and no sound can be heard within. Any creature or object within the sphere is immune to &amp;reference[thunder] damage. All creatures are &amp;reference[deafened] and &amp;reference[silenced] while inside. Casting a spell that includes a verbal component is impossible there.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Upcasting:</strong> The radius of the spell increases by 5 ft. for each spell level above 2nd level.</p>"
